This is actually the format I would use in a **professional engineering audit**. I'd also tweak the categories a bit because for a **Spring Boot microservice**, **Logging shouldn't be 10%**. I'd elevate **Observability** and add **Operational Readiness**.

Save this as `MICROSERVICE_AUDIT.md`.

